| volume=4
| issue=
| year=2008
| pages=71-81
| doi=10.1017/S1743921308026252 }}</ref>；而后续的多普勒光学研究则确认了它的存在。<ref name="followup">{{cite web
| title=Radial velocity follow-up for confirmation and characterization of transiting exoplanets
| url=http://arxiv.org/PS_cache/arxiv/pdf/0902/0902.3520v1.pdf
| author=Bouchy ''et al.''
| year=2008
| accessdate=2009-05-04
| archive-date=2020-09-20
